<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78d4f52e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s917b"><num value="917b">§ 917b.</num><heading> Cooperation of other Federal agencies</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All Federal agencies shall cooperate, to the fullest extent possible, with the Secretary of Commerce in preparing the study and recommendations required by <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s917a">section 917a of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78d4f52f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/94/532/s4">Pub. L. 94–532, § 4</ref>, <date date="1976-10-17">Oct. 17, 1976</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/90/2492">90 Stat. 2492</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
